Description: iSCSI, Fibre Channel and Multipath configuration plugin for Proxmox VE
 Adds iSCSI, Fibre Channel and multipath management panels to the Proxmox VE web GUI,
 including a datacenter-level setup wizard supporting both iSCSI and FC transports.
